@RegisterApp.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5185

### Health Check
GET {{RegisterApp.Api_HostAddress}}/api/health
Accept: application/json

###

### User Authentication
POST {{RegisterApp.Api_HostAddress}}/api/users/authenticate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "testpassword"
}

###

### User Registration
POST {{RegisterApp.Api_HostAddress}}/api/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "username": "johndoe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123"
}

###

### Get All Users
GET {{RegisterApp.Api_HostAddress}}/api/users
Accept: application/json

###

### Get User by ID
GET {{RegisterApp.Api_HostAddress}}/api/users/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Get All Visits
GET {{RegisterApp.Api_HostAddress}}/api/visits
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Available Visits
GET {{RegisterApp.Api_HostAddress}}/api/visits/available
Accept: application/json

###

### Add New Visit
POST {{RegisterApp.Api_HostAddress}}/api/visits
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startTime": "2026-05-01T10:00:00",
  "endTime": "2026-05-01T11:00:00",
  "patient": 0,
  "type": "General Checkup"
}

###

